{"tid":791314,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「人生必睇電影推介」- Taxi Driver 的士司機","createTime":"2018-08-23T16:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T08:56:39.000Z","uid":179096,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"44705a6bf942373d0f2c858a9de1471dfde3ee84","tid":791314,"uid":179096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/232224_9112a38d7b7b3d4bfeb32e087ea77ba9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F232224_9112a38d7b7b3d4bfeb32e087ea77ba9.png&h=c393334c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/232225_040c027d2cce78f7269929022155ac10.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F232225_040c027d2cce78f7269929022155ac10.png&h=777541a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年份：1976年<br />\n地區：美國<br />\n導演：馬丁&middot;史柯西斯 Martin Scorsese<br />\n編劇：保羅&middot;許瑞德 Paul Schrader<br />\n主演：勞勃&middot;狄尼洛 Robert De Niro <br />\n           茱蒂&middot;福斯特 Alicia Christian Foster<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚主觀非劇透推介原因：<br />\n<br />\n的士司機有幾撚經典唔洗我多講，但係𠵱一套係對我人生觀有好大影響嘅電影其中之一。如果你都係一個孤獨者，覺得社會充斥好多惡、偽善，我諗𠵱套戲可以帶俾你好大嘅共嗚。同埋導演常用嘅第一人稱嘅述事手法，大量內心ov令到觀眾更加入到個主角嘅內心世界。"},{"pid":"b0e5bc0807d00d67e7b54f5215e9f125ee5b28c5","tid":791314,"uid":27616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:30:51.000Z","msg":"You talking to me?"},{"pid":"5e96d73dd88fe7d2ed793f897628e20e86522041","tid":791314,"uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/093043_1c73bd96d4f577bad1e63dff7152ea7c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F093043_1c73bd96d4f577bad1e63dff7152ea7c.gif&h=7d762674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好撚short"},{"pid"